{"tid":2364695,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑心藥房改名開超市","createTime":"2021-01-13T07:28:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T12:06:31.000Z","uid":233098,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1c86b1dccd361995fe443c24afa0f2363bea0b4b","tid":2364695,"uid":233098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:28:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_773103_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_773103_0&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEfuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=a243ed2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_773103_0&h=a775335c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_773103_0</a><br />\n<br />\n曾被揭發賣假藥的龍豐藥房，多年來在自由行力撐下生意火紅，分店由上水開到尖沙咀達22間。身兼黑龍江政協的老闆謝少海，被冠以「藥房大王」之稱。同時他又覷準時機炒樓炒舖，豬籠入水，身家暴漲至逾八億，幾年前雄心壯志道：「我哋目標開50間分店！」<br />\n<br />\n只是，謝少海沒料到武漢肺炎緊接社運殺到，水貨客會有完全絕跡的一日。本刊統計，龍豐由2019年22間分店，縮至今年14間，當中上水更成重災區，八間剩四間。疫情下，謝少海意識到港人是「救命稻草」，開始轉做港人生意，就連位於上水的龍豐金舖員工，都稱自己「專做街坊生意」。<br />\n<br />\n上水旗艦藥房變超市<br />\n2019年11月，即社運爆發後第五個月，謝少海仍看好上水區前景，以每月55萬，租用最多水貨客掃貨的上水新康街地段舖位。該複式地舖連一樓，面積逾萬呎，租金比上一手高出足足52.8%。當時市場預料將是龍豐區内旗艦店，以三年租期計，總租金支出近二千萬元。<br />\n<br />\n後來肺炎肆虐，內地客源歸零，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">謝少海在去年初，將舖位轉開專做港人生意的超市「market88」。過往謝少海旗下的藥房、粉麵店、珠寶店均一律以「龍豐」為名。今次謝少海似乎有意洗底，超市沒有「龍豐」二字，Facebook更強調自己是「以社區為本的超級市場」，與美心、太興及富臨，將旗下食肆改名開分身的手法如出一轍。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rj22OLf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frj22OLf.png&h=de092812&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b4ebbd5b9f1a82932c89d5f6964e37068ea4703","tid":2364695,"uid":233098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"上水街坊請睇路"},{"pid":"56000d256bd0ddb03787bc715c24b69b2ae01d55","tid":2364695,"uid":330227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:40:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n笠水狗"},{"pid":"02d3c075bdb6ac0cea92a3f59067aa430e1b29ef","tid":2364695,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:49:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"874ecaa4559139315e133cdd91abffb2bcd89823","tid":2364695,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:51:24.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"67e7e8708f3dd062674bd932bddab31a9727c624","tid":2364695,"uid":138948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a0d8ff666ca932498e54cd09331326b8ca6f46","tid":2364695,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d8ee2ba674b8c6e8452631c5a9466f57b1e174","tid":2364695,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re